<br>
On your BC Christian Families board, where everyone would probably define themselves as &quot;fundamentalists&quot;, there are a select few who have earned the title &quot;fundie&quot; (and <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em>I</em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--> won't mention names, either <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :lol --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/laugh.gif ALT=":lol"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  but we all know they're lurking here, despite lengthy protestations to the contrary. . .)<br>
